I still get flashes of charming Pratyusha and her collector sahab, Siddharth.

snippet.textDisplay:
Balika Vadhu ( season 1 ) was a masterpiece. Every song in it and everything about it is just amazing. ❤️
Shiv and Anandi are my favourite couple.. but today both the actors ( Siddharth Shukla and Pratyusha Bannerjee ) who played the roles are no more with us...
Unhone hi to muje is gane se milwaya tha, nhi to pata nhi kbhi ise dekh, sunn aur feel kar bhi pati ya nhi, this song reminds me of them.. 🥺😭
